136
00:16:48,000 --> 00:17:00,000
Aded musaqefiyên gund pir in, meselen ihsaîya musaqefên gund
jî xwedan şehade, çend muhamî ne, çend doxtor in...
 
The number of intellectuals of the village is a lot, for
